put.description:
Whenever a change occurs in a room (whether it concerns occupancy or counting), the proxy can notify an external platform.

After each query, the changes will be sent to the configured webhook as a POST request with the following JSON body :
* For occupancy webhooks :
```{json}
[
  {
    spaceId: key,
    occupancy_status: newStatus,
    normalized_occupancy_status: newNormalizedStatus,
    occupancy_status_updated_at: modificationDate
  }, 
  ...
]
```
* For counting webhooks : 
```{json}
[
  {
    spaceId: key,
    count: number,
    count_updated_at: modificationDate
  }, 
  ...
]
```
